issue.title: Pictorial Answer to Who is Miriam?
issue.body:
Kid's13 and under keep asking for a picture of Miriam, so belonging to Elite Epic Game developers for the Unreal Engine 4. This is a test of the unreleased UE Character AI. The character code generator is superb 
Its licenced under the Unreal Engine licence which means its NOT GLPL or GLP, but available for use with the AWS SAM in this case the Miriam's Journey examples. Really no sure which folder this picture goes but to allow linking in the "largeImageUrl" entity in the StoryTable.
